_sText:
Hey there

This is a major upgrade to my previous map...

changes:
- there is alot more cover such as box's found on lowerlevel and upperlevel
- teleport room has been changed to sumwhat make sence
- a changed sound effect in the teleport room
- rather then a ramp leading to the teleport, 4 ladders in its place
- better lighting 
- added dust/fog to make the map seem more realistic
- spawn point a angles changed facing eachother

i have also changed the names of gg_mayhem to gg_tele_arena due to a clash with sumone elses map of the same name... this map however is diffrent.

i have lernt alot from my first map in such a short time and just that extra little work to the map has made a significant diffrence and i can see this being played alot. 

the basis of the map is the same..plain and simple and alot of clash between players = funner gameplay

* This map is available in both gg and normal css ( Buyzones available ) *

i really hope u like this map and give it ago, try it with your friends or servers and give me feed back of what u think or anything you would like

thanks alot 

Malphas :)
